{"tid":137160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"某些小巴佬聽嗌落唔舉手壞習慣 乞鳩憎","createTime":"2017-02-27T15:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T17:10:48.000Z","uid":47636,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d88beb5bf1c29811c29d98443ca61dc61321707","tid":137160,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊平時有舉手、只係間中聽唔到嗰啲好司機。就講啊叔坐開嗰架，有個小巴佬真係好撚濕鳩。屌你老味次撚次不論聽唔聽到人嗌落都唔柒會舉手，真係好摟屌。<br />\n<br />\n你聽到又唔舉手，班乘客撚知你到時曉唔曉停比佢地落？好啦到人地嗌多次有落，你就大大聲屌翻人話你聽到，你話係咪搞撚到大家都扯火先？<br />\n<br />\n嗱到你聽唔到冇舉手，人地坐開你架車以為你習慣唔舉手。咁你過站冇停到車，人地話你兩句，你又係屌翻人轉頭話聽唔到嘛，下次有落嗌大聲啲啦。你個腦到底諗乜鳩？<br />\n<br />\n好心你地養成翻個好習慣啦，大家開開心心收工翻屋企，係要搞串個PARTY。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話啊叔鍵盤戰士，啱啱先屌柒完條撚樣，啊叔後生幾年打柒你添啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138a91ee6c2dd342e52c2d0f105033d8448227a3","tid":137160,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"咪大撚大聲叫有落叫到佢應你囉"},{"pid":"983cfa955b016ba24085c34f97f9cf2f79453773","tid":137160,"uid":29382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"無錯 所以我盡量都唔搭小巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ba778c82b81c993e8ad017bd812f9c33029a10","tid":137160,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:04:11.000Z","msg":"扭下扭下架車真係好難舉 <br />\n依家有d司機你話街口有落佢會變左係講收到或者得 咁樣"},{"pid":"18f1e99f33d2b48a1f756d28f64372a36ca23aa7","tid":137160,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪大撚大聲叫有落叫到佢應你囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱啊，平時坐開嗰架小巴見係佢，知佢啲脾氣都廢事同佢曬口水，今日又過站先出聲屌完佢獲甘嘅，下次再係咁吖嗱我真係屌到佢應啊。"},{"pid":"5d3c15327303ffca5b0ccb3e23dafcf402a90a1e","tid":137160,"uid":22424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外國人識唔識搭van 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4298edd8a4b0489b89d7e556625925fa00a6fbd","tid":137160,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扭下扭下架車真係好難舉 <br />\n依家有d司機你話街口有落佢會變左係講收到或者得 咁樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好聲好氣大家咪開心囉係咪先，遇著呢啲好司機我落車前就一定會講翻聲唔該曬師傅先。"},{"pid":"db00e4ec42e40eed4c7c84a5ee65f336239706d4","tid":137160,"uid":57505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:10:59.000Z","msg":"完全明白，試過屌到佢爭啲落車隻秋"},{"pid":"3a8bb770194457498d134c6150e07ecb1ecee740","tid":137160,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無錯 所以我盡量都唔搭小巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你九成後生仔啦，其實你對啲閪人唔洗逃避嘅，要惡過佢。"},{"pid":"dfe13e22a51d4ed0b0dd8fe583ad5a01eebd0458","tid":137160,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:13:42.000Z","msg":"竟然夠膽嗌有落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1def3e3bad0385cae0169ba6aabd13c153d1392d","tid":137160,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:16:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外國人識唔識搭van 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果未搭過，唔識又硬要搭都冇辦法。兩個問題，一係佢唔識嗌落，一係司機唔識聽。試過有個鬼佬叫我幫佢嗌啦，我廢事嗌錯就叫咗坐後面個OL姐姐仔幫佢囉。坐小巴呢啲一次生兩次熟嘅啫。"},{"pid":"5850cfab9082c30580d752085eadc44ab0242e12","tid":137160,"uid":6455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外國人識唔識搭van 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果未搭過，唔識又硬要搭都冇辦法。兩個問題，一係佢唔識嗌落，一係司機唔識聽。試過有個鬼佬叫我幫佢嗌啦，我廢事嗌錯就叫咗坐後面個OL姐姐仔幫佢囉。坐小巴呢啲一次生兩次熟嘅啫。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見過外國人用英文叫有落<br />\n小巴司機答番佢ok"},{"pid":"1f718d2b8647c7d3debab580965d36f3ce853b32","tid":137160,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:33:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全明白，試過屌到佢爭啲落車隻秋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你後生仔打得唔怕啊，要我打就未必夠打，勝在我把口夠臭，哈哈哈"},{"pid":"4d00bea1ffddbb32ae5a1b27b198a696f6da6326","tid":137160,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外國人識唔識搭van 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果未搭過，唔識又硬要搭都冇辦法。兩個問題，一係佢唔識嗌落，一係司機唔識聽。試過有個鬼佬叫我幫佢嗌啦，我廢事嗌錯就叫咗坐後面個OL姐姐仔幫佢囉。坐小巴呢啲一次生兩次熟嘅啫。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見過外國人用英文叫有落<br />\n小巴司機答番佢ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能司機經驗老到，又可能鬼佬係熟客仔呢"},{"pid":"f3f7af03dfadaa85c40bc928840738aed3d7f3bb","tid":137160,"uid":60065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:23:16.000Z","msg":"唔示意真係唔知係咪聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw而家有d小巴咪有鐘仔禁，禁完係咪好似巴士咁會著燈？"},{"pid":"97f7872e45fca55fe1d45bdfed37046dd0507517","tid":137160,"uid":74145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:24:17.000Z","msg":"特別係通宵更最多<br />\n見到都會大叫2次邊到有落 佢屌番轉頭就瘋狂屌柒佢"},{"pid":"947c1006108a0e524bf7e35b6583d247a875f76b","tid":137160,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔示意真係唔知係咪聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw而家有d小巴咪有鐘仔禁，禁完係咪好似巴士咁會著燈？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新啲嘅有，我搭開翻屋企嗰條線未見。"},{"pid":"47860e9cd0567c643a2033f6290efa91d451fad0","tid":137160,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>特別係通宵更最多<br />\n見到都會大叫2次邊到有落 佢屌番轉頭就瘋狂屌柒佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係諗唔通點解舉舉手都懶，我意思係次撚次都唔舉嗰啲"},{"pid":"a9b4101fecb7d8da4ea473c5f119357613715919","tid":137160,"uid":74145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>特別係通宵更最多<br />\n見到都會大叫2次邊到有落 佢屌番轉頭就瘋狂屌柒佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係諗唔通點解舉舉手都懶，我意思係次撚次都唔舉嗰啲</blockquote><br />\n咁緊係次撚次唔舉都屌，我睇住佢成程無舉過就會落車專登大叫叫到佢應，通常都會屌番你轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373c893446e01016dac4255137d37ddda70a889e","tid":137160,"uid":29987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T17:51:07.000Z","msg":"咪臭係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔知你聽唔聽到<br />\n等等原來你聽唔到，過站我咪pk<br />\n唔通要扮男人聲叫多次有落咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05a37358c8dd443ef8e4094161fbf9f82236fb9","tid":137160,"uid":29947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:33:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然夠膽嗌有落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28fbbeff86a69d056ffe5de6be839a52ac2b15b","tid":137160,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:37:09.000Z","msg":"阿叔又係你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e62d6ab477e0c5b29b2fc1d36a4dffe12d8a32","tid":137160,"uid":75924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>竟然夠膽嗌有落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常都係坐到總站再行番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4136b883ad16614b9dc2a7b5b9918b41ddcf514","tid":137160,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>特別係通宵更最多<br />\n見到都會大叫2次邊到有落 佢屌番轉頭就瘋狂屌柒佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係諗唔通點解舉舉手都懶，我意思係次撚次都唔舉嗰啲</blockquote><br />\n咁緊係次撚次唔舉都屌，我睇住佢成程無舉過就會落車專登大叫叫到佢應，通常都會屌番你轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驚閪佢啊！"},{"pid":"b8762251f66a39906c19b8a1d38cc4d3acc4eb07","tid":137160,"uid":47636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪臭係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔知你聽唔聽到<br />\n等等原來你聽唔到，過站我咪pk<br />\n唔通要扮男人聲叫多次有落咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係女士，我真係好同情，陰公你地真係唔夠小巴佬惡。"}]}